#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/models/project_project.py:0
msgid ""
"The \"%(folder)s\" folder should either be in the \"%(company)s\" company "
"like this project or be open to all companies."
msgstr ""
"ໂຟນເດີ \"%(folder)s\" ຄວນຢູ່ໃນບໍລິສັດ \"%(company)s\" ຄືກັບໂຄງການນີ້ ຫຼື ເປີດໃຫ້ທຸກບໍລິສັດນຳໃຊ້ໄ"
"ດ້."

#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/models/documents_document.py:0
msgid ""
"The \"%s\" folder is required by the Project application and cannot be "
"archived."
msgstr "ໂຟນເດີ \"%s\" ແມ່ນຈຳເປັນສຳລັບແອັບພລິເຄຊັນໂຄງການ ແລະ ບໍ່ສາມາດຈັດເກັບໄດ້."

#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/models/documents_document.py:0
msgid ""
"This action can't be performed, as it would remove the folders used by the following projects:\n"
"%(projects)s\n"
"To continue, choose different folders for these projects."
msgstr ""
"ການດຳເນີນການນີ້ບໍ່ສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້, ເນື່ອງຈາກວ່າມັນຈະລຶບໂຟນເດີທີ່ໃຊ້ໂດຍໂຄງການຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:\n"
"%(projects)s\n"
"ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່, ໃຫ້ເລືອກໂຟນເດີອື່ນສຳລັບໂຄງການເຫຼົ່ານີ້."

#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/wizard/documents_operation.py:0
msgid "This document belongs to %(task)s."
msgstr "ເອກະສານນີ້ແມ່ນຂອງ %(task)s."

#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/models/documents_document.py:0
msgid ""
"This folder should remain in the same company as the \"%(project)s\" project"
" to which it is linked. Please update the company of the \"%(project)s\" "
"project, or leave the company of this folder empty."
msgstr ""
"ໂຟນເດີນີ້ຄວນຢູ່ໃນບໍລິສັດດຽວກັນກັບໂຄງການ \"%(project)s\" ທີ່ມັນເຊື່ອມໂຍງຢູ່. ກະລຸນາອັບເດດບໍລິສັດຂອງໂ"
"ຄງການ \"%(project)s\", ຫຼື ປ່ອຍໃຫ້ບໍລິສັດຂອງໂຟນເດີນີ້ຫວ່າງໄວ້."

#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/models/documents_document.py:0
msgid ""
"This folder should remain in the same company as the following projects to which it is linked:\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
"Please update the company of those projects, or leave the company of this folder empty."
msgstr ""
"ໂຟນເດີນີ້ຄວນຢູ່ໃນບໍລິສັດດຽວກັນກັບໂຄງການຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ທີ່ມັນເຊື່ອມໂຍງຢູ່:\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
"ກະລຸນາອັບເດດບໍລິສັດຂອງໂຄງການເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ, ຫຼື ປ່ອຍໃຫ້ບໍລິສັດຂອງໂຟນເດີນີ້ຫວ່າງໄວ້."

#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/models/documents_document.py:0
msgid "Uh-oh! The project app needs the \"%s\" folder, so you can’t delete it."
msgstr ""
"ໂອ້! ແອັບໂຄງການຕ້ອງການໂຟນເດີ \"%s\", ດັ່ງນັ້ນເຈົ້າຈຶ່ງບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບມັນໄດ້."

#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/models/documents_document.py:0
msgid "You cannot archive the project base folder (%s)."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າບໍ່ສາມາດຈັດເກັບໂຟນເດີຫຼັກຂອງໂຄງການ (%s) ໄດ້."

#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/models/project_project.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot change the company of this project, because its folder is linked to the other following projects that are still in the \"%(other_company)s\" company:\n"
"%(other_folders)s\n"
"\n"
"Please update the company of all projects so that they remain in the same company as their folder, or leave the company of the \"%(folder)s\" folder blank."
msgstr ""
"ເຈົ້າບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນບໍລິສັດຂອງໂຄງການນີ້ໄດ້, ເພາະວ່າໂຟນເດີຂອງມັນຖືກເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບໂຄງການອື່ນໆ ທີ່ຍັງຢູ່ໃນບໍລິສັ"
"ດ \"%(other_company)s\":\n"
"%(other_folders)s\n"
"\n"
"ກະລຸນາອັບເດດບໍລິສັດຂອງທຸກໂຄງການເພື່ອໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາຢູ່ໃນບໍລິສັດດຽວກັນກັບໂຟນເດີຂອງພວກເຂົາ, ຫຼື ປ່ອຍໃຫ້ບໍລິສັດ"
"ຂອງໂຟນເດີ \"%(folder)s\" ຫວ່າງໄວ້."

#. module: documents_project
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/documents_project/models/documents_document.py:0
msgid "You cannot set a company on the %s folder."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າບໍ່ສາມາດກຳນົດບໍລິສັດໃຫ້ກັບໂຟນເດີ %s ໄດ້."
